rename to oh_my_god;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;C:%5CUsers%5Cwww13%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20211120202200841.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20211120202200841&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
